The ADS Standard

A Standard Above Everything Else

Every companion raised under the American Doodle Standard undergoes a meticulous process of genetic screening, developmental care, and personalized preparation before joining your family.

🧬

Genetic Health Screening

Comprehensive DNA testing and health clearances for both parents, ensuring your companion inherits optimal health from verified, temperament-tested bloodlines.

🧠

Early Neurological Stimulation

Bio-sensor protocols from days 3–16 develop stronger neural pathways, creating calmer, more adaptable companions with enhanced stress tolerance and learning capacity.

♡

Temperament Matching

Personalized personality assessments paired with detailed household questionnaires ensure each companion is matched to the family environment where they'll thrive most naturally.

👨‍👩‍👧

Family Socialization

Structured exposure to children, household sounds, surfaces, and diverse environments creates a confident, well-adjusted companion ready for real-life integration from day one.

✨

Premium Nutrition & Grooming

Veterinarian-guided nutrition programs and professional grooming standards ensure every companion arrives in peak health with a beautifully maintained coat.

🎓

Foundation Training

Age-appropriate behavioral foundations including crate introduction, potty training fundamentals, and positive reinforcement conditioning begin before your companion leaves our care.

Concierge Delivery

White-Glove Delivery.
Nationwide.

Your companion's journey home is handled with the same care and precision as every other stage of their development.

Personal Hand Delivery
Your companion is personally delivered to your home by a trained ADS handler—never shipped in cargo. We fly or drive to you, ensuring a calm, stress-free transition.
Transition Support Kit
A comprehensive starter companion kit including nutrition plan, training continuation guide, comfort items, and veterinary records accompanies every delivery.
Ongoing Consultation
Post-delivery training guidance and behavioral consultation available to ensure your companion settles in beautifully and continues developing on the right foundation.
